SNOWCRACK SUITE
...

SnowCrack is a binary search based cracking tool.
SnowGen is a dictionary generator that follows the SnowCrack format.
DictToSnow is a dictionary generator that sources the passwords from other plaintext dictionaries (passwords separated by newline).
GenHash is a simple NTLM hash generator included for testing purposes.

...
Dictionary files follow this format:
HEAD|HASH|HASH|HASH÷PASSW¬PASSW¬PASSW

Where 'HEAD' is the first four characters of the hashes that follow it. 'HEAD' is removed from the hashes to conserve space.
...

Dictionary files are alphabetically sorted. To do this manually, use Python's sort() function.


